xrestop|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
xrestop: xrestop (X Resource Monitor)
xrestop:
xrestop: A utility to monitor application usage of X resources in the X Server,
xrestop: and display them in a manner similar to 'top'. This is a very useful
xrestop: utility for tracking down application X resource usage leaks.
xrestop:
xrestop: http://www.freedesktop.org/Software/xrestop
xrestop:
xrestop:
